       Megatron sees the charge sail towrds him. He curses and runs as the 
blast explodes behinde him. He is sent flying forward, slamming into 
Killfest, with a back smoking from the burn of the blast.

       Tankkor yells as he knee cap bursts from Marines shot, and also from 
the large amount of electricity. He thrashes, and fianlly frees himself, 
rolling away from Endbringer. Marine, meanwhile, extends his hand. A small 
tip slides from his wrist, it was tipped with a gas bullet. On contact it 
would release a knock out gas....but, in Endbringers case it just might send 
him into a violent coughing fit. Marine fired.

       Aerostreak drives his hands deeper into Grevens neck, using all of his 
strength to choke the bot. Tarantulas is slapped to the side, but, with 
Greven so close, he fires another batch of cluster missles at close range.

       Putnam, Venus, Akron, and Odiphious continue to follow Scyther. When 
they hit him, the energon gave a quick siloquette of his figure. It vanished, 
but gave them something to go on.
       They continued, all of them, to fire at Darkmouse and Scyther. Blue 
blasts of energon enegy lit up the skies.

       Jackle, Gremlin, Pheniox, and Nighteyes gather together, under cover. 
The odds agianst them is great. "Alright, split up and take these guys as far 
away from here as possible. We already took out Dollen...." Gremlin says, as 
he scans over a wound with a medkit.
       Nighteyes nodds, turns, and hauls south. Gremlin takes north, Pheniox 
goes west and jackle goes east.

       Hell Beast opened the door to look at Shockwave, "AH, sorry to keep 
you waiting. Please, come in."

       Rampage, Inferno, and Waspinator watch the display showing the battle. 
They shook thier heads. It was messy. 

--part1_d5.9731a7.27867a25_boundary
